{"tid":388784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想比私補中介佬呃 求巴打建議","createTime":"2017-09-05T16:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T14:14:54.000Z","uid":141450,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e68085bbf88328cfb9ca1fb9d6689775dcb3b7d","tid":388784,"uid":141450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"我係係街邊嗰啲街招招學生私補果d poster，搣咗張聯絡電話字條，返屋企自己WhatsApp個中介，問佢需唔需要補習老師，然後佢約我聽日去屋企屋企附近都m記，做個人資料登記，需要中學畢業證書 DSE成績 同埋大學學生證同埋身分證 （all副本）<br />\n想問呢d程序係咪正常 怕比人困。同埋中介通常抽幾多佣<br />\n.<br />\nps：佢宜家介紹左我今個星期日去幫學生補習 約左時間 <br />\n不過怕比人呃 。<br />\n其他文件我ok，但請問係咪一定要身分證副本？"},{"pid":"d294bf1b26aa737b329ae7631246cf27522de586","tid":388784,"uid":141450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:33:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67df31e014b20fa185df8b8f7f17c87d778575d5","tid":388784,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"信街招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10adf113f5152a160e05df2e3c4c36771bbbf124","tid":388784,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"多數 頭兩堂錢係佣金 有d可能4堂<br />\n<br />\n其實都有好多要dse 學生證 驚有人扮大學生or扮神科人 都聽過有報假比家長發現<br />\n<br />\n身份證都要 <br />\n<br />\n因為要保障個學生"},{"pid":"cf7dd78f552485de47a87f0dfbb0da9a2c59cedc","tid":388784,"uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:48:02.000Z","msg":"街招你預得$80/h左右 <br />\n<br />\n多數人都係上網搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做小學生都起碼$110/h<br />\n<br />\n中學就$150/h<br />\n<br />\n遠少少收$180 above<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cf463881c19c0a1db3f0b9f105f89c78644479","tid":388784,"uid":141450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddced04486c8